@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title Double satisfaction: one output, two obligations

rectangle "Attacker's transaction" as TX {
  package "Inputs" {
    [DEX pool UTXO\nValidator A:\n\"need an output with 100 USDx\"] as A
    [Lending pool UTXO\nValidator B:\n\"need an output with 100 USDx\"] as B
  }
  package "Outputs" {
    [ONE output\n100 USDx] as O
  }
}

A --> O : sees it, considers itself satisfied
B --> O : sees the SAME output, satisfied too

note bottom of O
  Both validators check "some output meets
  the condition", so a single 100 USDx output
  discharges two obligations. Fix: require YOUR
  specific output, tagged with a beacon token.
end note
@enduml
